WEBVTT

00:01:29.125 --> 00:01:31.184
Do you like my hands?

00:01:31.208 --> 00:01:33.518
They're expressive, yeah?

00:01:33.542 --> 00:01:36.018
Now look at your hands -- now go on.

00:01:36.042 --> 00:01:38.726
There's so much history recorded
through their touches

00:01:38.750 --> 00:01:43.309
and marks of the future
sketched on their palms.

00:01:43.333 --> 00:01:45.143
Sometimes hands grip tight,

00:01:45.167 --> 00:01:47.958
sometimes hands let go.

00:01:49.375 --> 00:01:51.768
What if I told you

00:01:51.792 --> 00:01:54.292
it's all going to come undone?

00:01:55.083 --> 00:01:56.476
Hm.

00:01:56.500 --> 00:01:58.226
Ladies and gentlemen

00:01:58.250 --> 00:02:00.768
and otherwise described,